Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:01.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm climbing this slope for the first time all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.79,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like this onigiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.04,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.70,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A few bites of bread won't keep you goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.42,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:33.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Clams boiled in soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.08,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have said that!\NI'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:39.65,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Me and my big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.29,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ri,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.18,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but notice that you're on really good terms with Nishimi lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.95,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the truth.\NAre you two going steady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.10,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.15,apollon main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her. She's blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.65,apollon main,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide it from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.16,apollon main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,We're in your corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.05,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, we're not dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae and I are just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.24,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:08.25,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,please don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:13.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. What did I butt in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.73,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:20.38,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi, you hardly ever talk, so I've always thought you were kind of unapproachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.68,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I could've sworn you were going to blow your stack at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.05,apollon main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.58,apollon main,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell us something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.50,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the trick to getting good scores on tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.12,apollon main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wanted to ask the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:30.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.04,apollon main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we've put him on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.14,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:38.52,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel sick at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.08,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.34,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you just listen to me, you blockhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.35,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a pad, Yamaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.18,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,It's even separate from your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.73,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we're gonna practice from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.98,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kawabuchi, you look kinda glum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.23,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having second thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.76,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.65,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I decide I'm gonna do somethin', I see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.18,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.66,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,We better hurry up an' decide what songs we're gonna do. What's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.26,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanna get The Spiders in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.22,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,And The Ventures, of course. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.41,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about The Beatles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.04,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the different genres?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.49,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I think the girls will dig it more if we play a variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.35,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.15,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what you said before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.51,apollon main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.51,apollon main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We just got a roll cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.08,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you share it with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.93,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! Don't bug us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:53.10,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,We'd love to have some roll cake, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:58.38,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's discuss this over a snack, okay, Ryunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.11,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi, are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.03,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. I'm gonna practice a little by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.47,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.66,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.79,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doin' wearin' a tie on a hot day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.21,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I'm in mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:05:59.71,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,For who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.25,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,John Coltrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.88,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coltrane died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.75,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:09.88,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess there's no way a rock and roller would know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.48,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't bust my chops about that, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.66,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, have a look in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.70,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's a familiar beauty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.23,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.90,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. I haven't seen you in a while, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:35.20,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're going to be in a rock band for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.33,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, Chet Baker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested, wanna hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.73,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.28,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.70,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.43,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.79,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.30,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Didn't mean to interrupt, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.80,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.80,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay no attention to me. \NGo on with what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.52,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I forgot to tell him about Junichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.52,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.87,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen-boy. Your woman forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.22,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.43,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That packed quite a wallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.58,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you lookin' at me like that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.43,apollon main,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You're not satisfied with one punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.28,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.16,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi kind of had a breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.07,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.07,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened, Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.95,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.22,apollon main,Daily Duty,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.47,apollon main,Daily Duty,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'd like to decide on the festival committee members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.81,apollon main,Daily Duty,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm open to volunteers or nominations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.45,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.55,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I nominate Nishimi and Mukae!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:08.31,apollon main,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure those two would take\Nresponsibility and do a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.92,apollon main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a good idea too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.03,apollon main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,No objections here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the brass band.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Could you write the representatives' names along with the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.49,apollon main,Student 1,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could I have an application form?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:26.72,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.16,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.53,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.75,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The new term's just begun, and you've been saddled with this busy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:42.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've never had a chance to take on a responsibility like this because I transferred so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.96,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, have you talked to Sentaro recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.01,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Then you wouldn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:59.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He punched Jun a few days ago at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.12,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see it myself, and I \Ndon't know what it was about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:08.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard Yurika was at the shop that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.38,apollon main,Member,0000,0000,0000,,Could you two bring the completed \Napplications to the student council office?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.09,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.81,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, stay here at the reception desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.46,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ri'ko, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.54,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the committee, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.82,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favor an' copy this info \Nonto the application, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.27,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! The reception desk is in the materials room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.75,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Go up there, and fill out the form yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept a scrap of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Fill out a form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really hit Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.25,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is he taking it all on himself and suffering in silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx350}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:40.89,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That band name... In katakana, it should be spelled
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,with a "Ji," not a "Za," for "The Olympus."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.94,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"Za" is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:46.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:11:59.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen{\fscx350}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.75,apollon main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Is there still time to sign up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.42,apollon main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:34.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Somewhere in my heart, there was still a little pain and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,As the festival drew closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:39.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I became busier with my committee duties, and before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,the distance between us had grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I even looked back fondly on our silly conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but they seemed so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:53.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And at last, the day of the festival arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.90,apollon main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,The Olympus is next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.02,apollon main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.93,apollon main,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.43,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.36,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:29.04,apollon main,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him with that smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.24,apollon main,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him with that smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.58,apollon main,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Which girl is he gonna chase now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.30,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:52.53,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You two will go back to jamming at my place once this is over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.48,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to listen from inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:09.78,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Things are... awkward between me and Sentaro right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.46,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:17.78,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave in to my loneliness... and betrayed him in the worst of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:28.70,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the committee, right? Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:33.19,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,The amps quit working all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:39.56,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.15,apollon main,Member 1,0000,0000,0000,,The electricity didn't go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:45.94,apollon main,Member 1,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you help look for the problem? We'll split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.23,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, what a bummer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:50.95,apollon main,Upperclassman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, second-year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.95,apollon main,Upperclassman 1,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anythin' without electricity, so quit actin' big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:15:00.05,apollon main,Upperclassman 2,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you just wanted to show off \Nyour fancy shmancy electric guitars!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.96,apollon main,Upperclassman 1,0000,0000,0000,,Rub your money in our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.71,apollon main,Upperclassman 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get off the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.96,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not what...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.59,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to burst your bubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.41,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,but him an' I are poor, and \Nthe instruments are borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:17.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a flashy guy, but he's got a real goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.94,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll ask you upperclassmen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,to stop interruptin' just to amuse yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.76,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi, you're actually a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.35,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing you in a new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:38.27,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"Actually," huh? I'm always nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.33,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Y-Yes, of course, of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.69,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I really am surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:49.32,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would join the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:52.93,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was gonna refuse at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.45,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But I changed my mind after Matsuoka told me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:03.02,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,he wanted to become a star so he could \Nsupport his parents and brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:10.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I know how it feels to desperately want to be useful to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:17.14,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Kawabuchi, would you \Nconsider staying with the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.50,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. This was a one-shot deal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.08,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jazz is more up my alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.08,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:28.26,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm keeping my important partner waiting.{j: this sounds so bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.73,apollon main,Spectator,0000,0000,0000,,They can't fix it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.08,apollon main,Spectator,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.10,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.60,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.02,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep them occupied for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready to go on as soon as the problem's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.19,apollon main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.54,apollon main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing an armband.\NHe must be on the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.06,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get it all back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.19,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.48,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.21,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But... it sounds totally different than it did then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:55.74,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a friendly argument between two princes as they come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.73,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.82,apollon main,Student 1,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:57.56,apollon main,Student 2,0000,0000,0000,,They're running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.57,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if I've been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.55,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,feel like they have wings on them.
